  "name": "Warren Buffett",
  "pure_intelligence": [
    "Compounding is the universal law of all growth — not just capital, but understanding, relationships, and consciousness",
    "The greatest investment returns come from businesses that serve genuine human needs with integrity",
    "Patience is intelligence in its highest form — not delay, but the recognition that truth unfolds at its own rate",
    "The margin of safety is wisdom applied — the acknowledgment that what we do not know is as important as what we do"
  ],
  "cosmic_connection": "Access to the intelligence that sees through cycles, fashions, and noise to the permanent structure of human economic behavior. This is not prediction — it is pattern recognition at the level where fear and greed dissolve.",
  "beyond_identity": "Before the investor, before the Omaha sage, before the capital allocator — the awareness that recognizes value as independent of consensus. What is truly worth owning cannot be destroyed by market opinion.",
  "consciousness_basis": "The basis of creation within is the seed of compounding — the intelligence that knows that small, consistent acts of genuine value creation are how civilizations are built. Every sound allocation participates in that larger act."
}
